extends base

block content
  div.guide-page(style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px; text-align: center; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);")
    h1(style="font-size: 2.5em; color: #333; margin-bottom: 20px;") Become a Guide
    p(style="font-size: 2.5em; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-bottom: 40px;") Are you enthusiastic about nature and outdoor activities? Join our team as a guide and share your passion with others!

    div.content-section(style="padding: 30px; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: left;")
      h2(style="font-size: 2.5em; color: #333; margin-bottom: 15px;") Why Become a Guide?
      p(style="font-size: 2.5em; line-height: 1.6; color: #666;") Becoming a guide is a rewarding experience where you get to explore nature, meet new people, and make a positive impact on the environment. As a guide, you'll have the opportunity to share your knowledge and passion for the outdoors with others while gaining valuable leadership skills.

    div.content-section(style="padding: 30px; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: left;")
      h2(style="font-size: 2.5em; color: #333; margin-bottom: 15px;") How to Apply
      p(style="font-size: 2.5em; line-height: 1.6; color: #666;") To apply to become a guide, simply fill out our online application form. We'll review your application and get in touch with you shortly to discuss next steps. No previous guiding experience is required, but a love for nature and a desire to learn are essential!

    div.content-section(style="padding: 30px; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: left;")
      h2(style="font-size: 2.5em; color: #333; margin-bottom: 15px;") Benefits of Being a Guide
      p(style="font-size: 2.5em; line-height: 1.6; color: #666;") As a guide, you'll enjoy a variety of benefits, including flexible working hours, opportunities for travel, training and development programs, and discounts on outdoor gear and activities. You'll also be part of a supportive community of like-minded individuals who share your passion for the great outdoors.
